00:05:41,000 --> 00:05:43,000
These are not wave equations because

114
00:05:43,000 --> 00:05:45,000
they have a plus sign there.

115
00:05:45,000 --> 00:05:49,000
These are electrostatic equations,

116
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:52,000
and they don't describe wave motion.

117
00:05:52,000 --> 00:05:54,000
You have to add, if you want waves,

